snippet.title: Master System Longplay [089] SDI: Strategic Defense Initiative
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by MadMatty

This probably the most difficult versin if played of this. So much to shoot, and the crosshair just crawls around the screen.

I've aimed to get perfect in every round to get max bonus so you dont get to see any defensive rounds. I was hopeing there would be a special unlock at the end involving Flicky, but...nothing. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
